content.html:
Boosted:

Saturn. September, 13 2017. Fond memory: During the Cassini Grand Finale on the night the spacecraft was to descend into the planet and end the mission, I was sitting at my desk at JPL waiting for this image data to come down. As soon as it did, I went running outside to some friends who were there for the media event and showed them, admiring the raw images on my phone. Then I went running back to my desk to start processing it. NASA/JPL/SSI/CICLOPS/Kevin M. Gill #Space #Science #Astrodon
content.value:
Boosted:Saturn. September, 13 2017. 

Fond memory: During the Cassini Grand Finale on the night the spacecraft was to descend into the planet and end the mission, I was sitting at my desk at JPL waiting for this image data to come down. As soon as it did, I went running outside to some friends who were there for the media event and showed them, admiring the raw images on my phone. Then I went running back to my desk to start processing it. 

NASA/JPL/SSI/CICLOPS/Kevin M. Gill

#Space #Science #Astrodon

content.html:
If you are a Mastodon user you might want to grab this bookmarklet to help you share web pages to Mastodon easier. You simply go to the page below, put in the address of your Mastodon instance it creates a Bookmarklet you can drag to your browser bar to make a button us can use anytime. Then, when you are on a page you want to share, select some text if you want and click the button. You'll get a pop up window that lest you start composing your Mastodon Toot right away.

Mastodon Toot Bookmarklet https://rknightuk.github.io/mastodon-toot-bookmarklet/

Mastodon user @rmlewisuk@toot.rodeo is the author of this tool.

Share and enjoy!
